    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape for all your upcoming adventures! It runs super smoothly and has been really well-loved, so it's ready for you to just hop in and go. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that feels great on the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to help you get behind the wheel!",
