    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound example of this iconic platform, optimized for the driving purist. This vehicle features a high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant mated to a crisp short-throw manual gearbox, delivering linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on lateral stability, utilizing stiffened bushings and a limited-slip differential to ensure maximum traction through the apex. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a fresh fluid flush. The exterior retains its aerodynamic profile with minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, while the interior remains focused and functional. This is a turn-key machine for someone who values visceral feedback and balanced handling dynamics over a trailer-queen status.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
