    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a well-preserved enthusiast car. Finished in its original factory paint, the exterior retains a deep gloss, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats remain supple with only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s side, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracks. All electronic components, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the brake pads have plenty of life and the tires are at approximately 70% tread. The transmission shifts smoothly without hesitation, and the engine pull is strong and consistent. It comes with two keys, the original owner's manual, and a folder of maintenance receipts. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner.",
